node.text:
Here's your guide to getting your SCUF controller set up to play like a pro in #ApexLegends.

For more info:
http://scufgaming.com/apex

node.title: Best Gaming Controller Guide: Apex Legends | How to SCUF

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by SCUF on September 03, 2021. May be an image of controller and text that says 'CUSTOMIZATION + REMOVABLE FACEPLATE IONIISNE SCUF'.

node.text: Tired of showing up with the same controller as everyone else? Customize it with millions of combinations and removeable faceplates.

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by SCUF on September 01, 2021. May be an image of text that says 'HIGH-PERFORMANCE GRIP'.

node.text: Flip the script. Let the controller hold you.

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by SCUF on August 30, 2021. May be an image of 2 people and text.

node.text: Milliseconds matter to us. It's the difference between being on the money or unlucky.

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by SCUF on August 27, 2021. May be an image of text that says 'PADDLE PROFILES + REMAPPPING B Y'.

node.text: Say goodbye to the pause 	menu. Easily swap between paddle mappings with up to three saved paddle profiles.

Get the jump on the competition. 
Flip to instant triggers.
	🔴---------------🟢 Default trigger
	🔴---🟢 Instant trigger

Whether it’s gaming or studying on on your tablet, poor posture can affect your performance.
Play smarter, not harder with an EXO SCUF. Now 20% off through the end of the month.

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by SCUF on August 24, 2021. May be an image of text that says 'S'.
Photo by SCUF on August 23, 2021. May be an image of 1 person and text.

node.text: Milliseconds matter to us. It's why some of us can recount our first tactical nuke (or 100th) while others are haunted by them.

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by SCUF on August 23, 2021. May be an image of text.

node.text: Paddles have defined our history. Now we have redefined them for the future.

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by SCUF on August 20, 2021. May be an image of controller.

node.text:
The Better. The Faster. 
Meet the new SCUF Instinct and SCUF Instinct Pro.
